---
title: Meatballs in Retro Chili Sauce with Buttered Rice
description: This tangy, sweet tomato-chili sauce will remind you of the meatballs your gran used to make, but instead of using sauce from a jar, it's made from scratch! Spoon it over golden beef and pork meatballs and buttery garlic rice for a nostalgic feast!
